room_title: Escape room "Fox Tail Saloon" by NorCal Escape Co. in Yuba City
room_description: Local legend has it, after a stagecoach heist, in an attempt to elude authorities, Billy the Kid stashed his loot in a nearby Saloon, only to be gunned down before he could return to claim it. Now recognized as a Historical Landmark, the Fox Tail Saloon has reopened its doors to those who seek the infamous outlaw's fortune.
